                     <interp inst="t17981024-50-off265" type="offenceSubcategory" value="bigamy"></interp>
               that he, on the 5th of December, in the parish of St. James, Westminster, in the 16th year of his present Majesty, took to wife 
                     
                        <persName id="t17981024-50-victim394" type="victimName">
                           Mary 
                           Goodall
                        <interp inst="t17981024-50-victim394" type="surname" value="Goodall"></interp>
